s\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my friends\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And because I loved the sport, I wanted to learn more, so I started training.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This pulled me in, and as I learnt new things that intrigued me--from technique to the skill--I decided to dive deeper.\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new things\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"technique\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"the skill\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After that, there was no looking back,\\\" he shared.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Subba first started training, he did not like following nutritional diets and hated waking up in the mornings.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Subba\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"nutritional diets\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the mornings\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the bigger issue arose when his training started affecting his academics; because of the grueling training that he had to go through every day, he would usually end up sleeping in class.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bigger issue\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"his training\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"his academics\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1711}, {\"ngram\": \"the grueling training\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"every day\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"class\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But no matter the cost, Subba stayed strong in 